OL,3,CCalls to improve A69 after another
OL,4,Clorry hits house
OL,6,FA bed and breakfast owner in a
OL,7,Fpicturesque Cumbrian village has
OL,8,Fdescribed her horror after a wagon
OL,9,Fploughed onto her property. Deborah
OL,10,FWearing was in her kitchen at teatime
OL,11,Fon Friday when she heard the lorry
OL,12,Fcome off the carriageway, onto the
OL,13,Fpavement, and into her garden. She
OL,14,Ftold ITV Border, "The noise was
OL,15,Fhorrendous but as soon as you hear it
OL,16,Fyou know exactly what it is because
OL,17,Fit's happened that many times before."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
