PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778771468
OL,3,CCalls to improve A69 after another
OL,4,Clorry hits house
OL,6,FMrs Wearing has lived in the house in
OL,7,FWarwick Bridge all her life, her
OL,8,Fmother was also born there. Since
OL,9,Fthen, she says she's lost count of how
OL,10,Fmany times traffic has struck her
OL,11,Fproperty. "To see a forty tonne wagon
OL,12,Fon its side, wedged up against your
OL,13,Fhouse is awful".
OL,15,FA structural engineer was called to
OL,16,Fassess the building which appears to
OL,17,Fhave narrowly escaped damage.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
