PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778771468
OL,3,CCalls to improve A69 after another
OL,4,Clorry hits house
OL,6,FThe neighbour opposite described how
OL,7,Fthe impact of Friday's crash caused
OL,8,Ftiles to fall off his roof. He says he
OL,9,Fcan still smell diesel from the 40
OL,10,Ftonne wagon.
OL,12,FThis latest accident, which Cumbria
OL,13,FPolice are still investigating, has
OL,14,Fprompted fresh calls to de-trunk part
OL,15,Fof the busy A69 Carlisle to Newcastle
OL,16,Froad and introduce weight limits that
OL,17,Fcould divert HGVs. Campaigners are
OL,18,Falso calling for the speed limit
OL,19,Fthrough Warwick Bridge to be lowered
OL,20,Ffrom 30 mph to 20 mph.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
