OL,3,CCalls to improve A69 after another
OL,4,Clorry hits house
OL,6,FOne of the campaigners, Councillor
OL,7,FRoger Dobson, told ITV Border, "This
OL,8,Fis another serious accident, one of
OL,9,Fseveral we've had in recent years.
OL,10,FThis is completely unnecessary because
OL,11,Fthe road is unsuitable for heavy goods
OL,12,Fvehicles."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
