OL,3,CCalls to improve A69 after another
OL,4,Clorry hits house
OL,6,FIn 2019, to help improve safety in
OL,7,Fvillages along the route, average
OL,8,Fspeed cameras were installed. In a
OL,9,Fstatement National Highways said "We
OL,10,Fare continuing to work with the
OL,11,FCumbria Road Safety Partnership to
OL,12,Fkeep this route as safe as possible
OL,13,Ffor everyone who uses it." ITV Border
OL,14,Fhas also approached Cumberland Council
OL,15,Fand the Department for Transport for
OL,16,Fcomment.
